data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT !! Totally Upgraded. Upscale Subdivision w Beautiful 132 acre Nature Preserve w camp grounds, ATV trails, walking trails, Large Fishing Pond W Pier, water falls over flowing natural Rock.Wide Concrete streets and all 1 acre lots. Barely lived in.4 bedroom,2 bath, 2 dining room home has a 3 car garage. Coat closet. Kitchen has a gorgeous extra large granite breakfast bar with a sink. Custom cabinets. Pantry. The Primary Bedroom is large and has a bath with walk in closet with tall ceilings for 3 rows of hanging space. Separate tub and The large tile walk in shower has a bench.Double granite counter tops and sinks. Plank Tile floors. Exterior is Stone, 100 percent Brick, Gutters. 9 x 15 Covered back patio. The town of Blue Ridge has a grocery store, schools, restaurants, and is the home of the Blue Ridge Rodeo. A short drive to Farmersville where there is also popular restaurants, and shopping. DFW International airport is aprx 1 hr drive.Be in McKinney in minutes.
